title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 5 2022
description:
Secret Service rents multimillion-dollar mansion in Malibu to protect Hunter Biden. Buck says in that case he wishes he were in the Secret Service. Clay wonders if anyone protected by the Secret Service was ever indicted. NYC Mayor Adams fires city attorney and mom Daniela Jampel, who stood up to him on masks at press conference. Former Assistant Treasury Secretary under President Trump Monica Crowley talks to Clay and Buck about the disastrous Biden economic policies. Will Elon Musk be the man who saves Twitter? C&B say they are feeling respect for Musk regarding his Twitter moves so far.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
